# Context Questionnaire

This file is a guided interview. Run `/setup-context` (or any agent that
reads this file) and it will walk you through the questions below,
writing your answers into the `### Answer` block under each section.

You can also fill it in by hand — workflows read the `### Answer` blocks
and ignore the question / format / example scaffolding.

**Free-form text is fine.** Workflows pass your answers to an LLM, which
extracts whatever structure it needs (industries, competitors, ICP
tiers, etc.). Don't worry about formatting — write like you'd explain
it to a teammate.

**On re-run:** the agent will ask, section by section, whether to
**keep** the existing answer, **append** to it, or **replace** it. Your
call each time.

Copy this file to `context.md` in the same folder. `context.md` is
gitignored so your real positioning never gets committed.

---

## Product

**Question:** What's the product? Name, one-liner, and website.

**Used by:** every workflow

**Example answer:**
> Carnival — an AI-native CRM that auto-fills pipeline data from email
> and calendar so reps stop doing data entry. usecarnival.com.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

