## Disqualifiers

**Question:** What kind of companies or personas should be excluded
entirely? Industries you don't sell to, company sizes that don't fit,
red flags that mean "skip this lead."

**Used by:** every lead-finding workflow

**Example answer:**
> Skip: agencies, consultancies, sub-5-person companies, anyone
> regulated (healthcare, banking, gov), companies on a homegrown CRM
> we can't integrate with, anyone who churned out of a competitor in
> the last 6 months.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

