## Competitors

**Question:** Who are your direct competitors and what's your edge
against each one?

**Used by:** competitor_analysis · email_outreach (positioning)

**Example answer:**
> HubSpot — we win on automation depth (they're a system of record;
> we're a system of action). Attio — we win on the AI-native data
> entry; they win on customization. Folk — we win on enterprise
> readiness; they win on simplicity for solo founders.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

