## Tone of voice

**Question:** How should outreach copy sound? Formal or casual?
Technical or plain? Long or short? Any words / phrases you want
banned?

**Used by:** email_outreach · linkedin_outreach · linkedin_comment_helper · blog_builder

**Example answer:**
> Casual, plain English, short. No "synergy," "leverage," "unlock,"
> "in this fast-paced world," or any LinkedIn-influencer cadence.
> Sound like a peer DMing another founder — not a vendor.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

