# Workflow-specific extras

These sections are only needed if you plan to run the matching
workflow. Skip anything irrelevant.

---

## Blog Goals & Topics

**Question:** Who's the audience for your blog, what tone do you
want, and what kinds of posts should the workflow generate? Be
specific — vague answers produce vague posts.

**Used by:** blog_builder

**Example answer:**
> Audience: engineering managers at Series-A AI companies. Tone:
> practical, no-fluff, opinionated. Topics: evals, infra costs, team
> patterns, when to build vs buy. Never thought-leadership puffery,
> never "5 ways to..." listicles.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

