## Blog Reference Sources

**Question:** Whose blogs do you want this workflow to model after,
by style or depth? One per line, format `Name | domain.com`.

**Used by:** blog_builder

**Example answer:**
```
Anthropic | anthropic.com
Cursor | cursor.com
Pylon | usepylon.com
```

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

