# Which sections each workflow needs

| Section | Workflows |
|---|---|
| Product · Who it's for | every workflow |
| Ideal Customer Profile | competitor_analysis · email_outreach · linkedin_outreach · signal_based_lead_outreach · icp_activity_tracker |
| ICP Segments | email_outreach |
| Right buyers · Decision-maker titles · Champion titles | email_outreach · linkedin_outreach |
| LinkedIn Post Relevance Filter | linkedin_outreach |
| Disqualifiers | every lead-finding workflow |
| Competitors | competitor_analysis · email_outreach |
| Tone of voice | email_outreach · linkedin_outreach · linkedin_comment_helper · blog_builder |
| Blog Goals & Topics · Blog Reference Sources | blog_builder |
| LinkedIn Comment Genre / Signal Keywords | linkedin_comment_helper |

The **content_idea_finder** workflow has its own questionnaire at
`workflows/content_idea_finder/content.md.example` — its inputs are
content-strategy decisions, not GTM context, so they live next to the
workflow.
